quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  22,6,"Ɗum, ko tawde pellet, Alla ko Kaŋko woni Goonga kan, pellet, O wurtinat maayɓe ɓen, tawde pellet, ko O kattanɗo e dow kala hu'unde."
  22,7,"Pellet, Darngal ngal ko aray ngal sikke alaa e maggal, won'de pellet, Alla immintinay ɓen won'ɓe ka genaale."
  22,8,"No e yimɓe ɓen on mo no weeñdaa e fii Alla ko aldaa e ganndal wonaa peewal wonaa deftere nurɗunde(jalbunde)."
  22,9,"Hkfɗo balaaji mu'un [mawnintiniiɗo] fii yo o majjin gah Laawol Alla ngol, no woodani mo ka aduna koyeere Min meeɗinoyay mo kadi Ñande Darngal Lepte cumoowe ngen."
  22,10,"Ɗum ko sabu ko juuɗe maaɗa ɗen ngardini kon. E won'de pellet, Alla wonaani Tooñoowo jeyaaɓe ɓen."
  22,11,"No e yimɓe ɓen on mo no rewa Alla e dow selindaare; si moƴƴere heɓii mo o tabitira sabu ɗuum si jarrabuyee kadi heɓii mo o waylitoo e ye'eso makko, o hayrii aduna on e La'akara on ko ɗum tigi woni hayrere ɓanngunde nden."
  22,12,"Homo rewa gah Alla ko lorrataa mo e ko nafataa mo kadi. Ɗuum [ko jaŋtaa ɗoo], ko ɗum woni majjere woɗɗunde nden."
  22,13,"Homo rewa on mo lorra mum no ɓuri ɓadaade diini nafa mum kan, bonii welddiɗo bonii kadi wuuridaaɗo."
  22,14,"Pellet, Alla homoo naatna ɓen gooŋɗinɓe ɓe ngolli moƴƴi ɗin Aljannaaji no ila sengo ley majji caatlii ɗi, pellet, Alla homo waɗa ko o faandii ko."
  22,15,"On gonɗo no sikka won'de Alla wallataa mo ka aduna e ka La'akara; yo o fortu ɓoggol fa'ade ka kammu refti o taƴa ngol yo o ndaaru taw si pewje makko ɗen ittay ko tikkani ko."